===Rexx Symposium Presentations on Object REXX===

Here are some links to presentations made at various Rexx Symposia that are related to Object REXX:

* [http://rexxla.org/Symposium/2004/abstracts.html#ronyf1 Object Rexx and Windows Automation Interfaces - Rony Flatscher (2004)]
* [http://rexxla.org/Symposium/2004/abstracts.html#davida Object Rexx GTK+ Project - David Ashleyr (2004)]
* [http://rexxla.org/Symposium/2004/abstracts.html#larry Concurrency with Object Rexx - Lavrentios Servissoglou (2004)]
* [http://rexxla.org/Symposium/2004/abstracts.html#michaelw DATERGF: From Rexx to Java to Object Rexx - Michael Warmuth (2004)]

